---
import Boton from "../components/boton.astro";
import Principal from "../layout/principal.astro";
---

<Principal title="Home">
  <div class="contenedor_principal">
    <div class="contenedor_character contenedores_internos">
      <img src="../../public/Main/Fondo_character.jpg" alt="" />
      <div class="descripcion_character">
        <p class="title">Characters</p>
        <p class="descripcion">
          The characters in "Rick and Morty" are a blend of humans, aliens, and
          bizarre creatures, each with unique and often eccentric personalities.
          As the plot progresses, these characters build intricate relationships
          and find themselves immersed in situations that can be both absurd and
          potentially dangerous.
        </p>
        <Boton name="Character" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="contenedor_locations contenedores_internos">
      <img src="../../public/Main/Fondo_location.jpg" alt="" />
      <div class="descripcion_character">
        <p class="title">Locations</p>
        <p class="descripcion">
          The locations in "Rick and Morty" encompass a wide array of settings,
          spanning from distant planets and alternate dimensions to bizarre
          realms. Each place is distinct and often showcases surreal landscapes
          or peculiar environments. As the series unfolds, these locations serve
          as the backdrop for the characters' adventures, offering both
          fantastical and sometimes perilous scenarios.
        </p>
        <Boton name="Location" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="contenedor_episode contenedores_internos">
      <img src="../../public/Main/Fondo_episodes.png" alt="" />
      <div class="descripcion_character">
        <p class="title">Episodes</p>
        <p class="descripcion">
          "Rick and Morty" is a series that spans multiple seasons, each with
          its own storyline and set of episodes. Throughout the seasons, viewers
          witness the increasingly extravagant and often chaotic adventures of
          Rick and Morty as they explore alternate dimensions, time travel, and
          confront a variety of cosmic challenges.
        </p>
        <Boton name="Episode" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Principal>

<style>
  .contenedor_principal {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .contenedores_internos {
    padding: 40px;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 10vh 0;
    color: var(--letras);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-evenly;
    font-size: 20px;
  }

  .title {
    font-size: 2em;
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-family: Get Schwifty;
    color: var(--vrd_clr);
  }

  .descripcion {
    font-size: 0.9em;
    font-family: "Montserrat", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .contenedor_character,
  .contenedor_episode {
    flex-direction: row-reverse;
  }

  img {
    width: 50%;
    height: 50%;
    border-radius: 2em;
  }

  .descripcion_character {
    width: 40%;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 990px) {
    img {
      width: 90%;
    }

    .contenedores_internos {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .descripcion_character {
      width: 90%;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }

    .descripcion {
      font-size: 1.2em;
    }
  }
</style>
